data.description: Live TALL and discover modern elegance in this beautiful 3 year young townhome in the conveniently located The Enclave at Belmont community.  This 3 story end unit offers beautiful curb appeal with its own private and gated street access and front yard.  As you enter the garden level, you are met with two bedrooms and a full bathroom featuring shower/tub combo and modern bidet.  The main level opens to a beautiful sunlit open concept with gorgeous white kitchen cabinets and a large quartz countertop island.  The kitchen flows into an open living and dining space perfect for entertaining.  The primary bedroom offers a luxurious and stylish suite with a spa like bathroom with large shower and soaking tub.  The upper floor features an oversized loft space which offers flex space opportunities such as work from home, fitness, and so much more.  Enjoy and unwind with community amenities featuring sparking pool, club house, and dog walk.  The community is such a special location that offers a "Village" like area with several shops, restaurants, and boutiques right outside your front door!
